<br>
SELECT * FROM orders
ORDER BY order_date
LIMIT 10;
<br>
    Breakdown of what's happening:
    <em>Select *</em> (Show all)
    <em>From</em> (the table labled orders)
    <em>Order</em> by (Setting the list to be in order by date)
    <em>Limit</em> (Limits the output of lines, in this case we set it to 10.)

